OL,7,FEnergy firms could use bailiffs to
OL,8,Fcome after cars and TVs from
OL,9,Fstruggling customers as a result of
OL,10,Fthe ban on prepayment meters, an
OL,11,Fenergy industry source has told i.
OL,13,FRegulator Ofgem announced a new code
OL,14,Fof practice which bans energy
OL,15,Fcompanies from forcibly installing
OL,16,Fprepayment meters (PPMs) in certain
OL,17,Fhouseholds, including where people
OL,18,Fare aged over 85 or rely on medical
OL,19,Fequipment such as a dialysis machine.
